						<summary>

						<p>The inscription is built in at the end. It records a gift of gold for burning a perpetual lamp in the temple of Mūlasthāṉattu Mahādēva of Śrī Āṟṟuttaḷi with the interest thereon, by a private individual whose name is not clear.</p>						

